### **4. 24_StreamScopeGrid**  
**Description:**  
Visualizes real-time numeric data from multiple streams on a scrolling live chart.

#### **README.md**
```markdown
# StreamScopeGrid - Realtime Multi-Stream Chart Viewer

StreamScopeGrid transforms live metrics or simulation outputs into a grid-based scrolling chart.

## Features
- Multi-stream live charting  
- Adjustable refresh rate  
- Matplotlib visualization  

## Usage
```bash
git clone https://github.com/your-username/24_StreamScopeGrid.git
cd 24_StreamScopeGrid
python visualize.py
